Required packages:

python3
python3-pygame

Debian (Raspbian) comes with pygame installed.
To hide Raspberry mouse cursor, under Raspbian with lightdm and LXCE,
edit the file /etc/ligthdm/lightdm.conf and add:

[SeatDefaults]
xserver-command = X -nocursor

To autorun on LXCE add 'LinguaMae.desktop' to ~/.config/autostart

-----

Fedora 24 install:

 $ sudo dnf install python3 python3-pygame


